{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "3fff4543-2e62-40df-872a-52f6eabb9af2", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3fff4543-2e62-40df-872a-52f6eabb9af2@1.pkg/1772597619482/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597619693", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3fff4543-2e62-40df-872a-52f6eabb9af2@1.pkg/1772597619482/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597619693"}, "identifier": "3fff4543-2e62-40df-872a-52f6eabb9af2", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B项错误：&ldquo;完全自主可控&rdquo;表述绝对化，题干提到&ldquo;技术依赖风险&rdquo;，说明仍有短板。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A项：重庆站台升级体现科技惠民。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C项：央企AI场景印证科技对综合国力的作用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D项：机器人大会数据反映中国创新实力。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>2025年，中国科技创新持续突破。以下新闻评述中，错误的是（　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）2025年，中国科技创新持续突破。以下新闻评述中，错误的是（　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3fff4543-2e62-40df-872a-52f6eabb9af2@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754626261393", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>2025年1月，重庆智能公交站台升级至3.0版，新增AI语音助手和太阳能无线充电，日均服务超10万人次&mdash;&mdash;科技创新让城市生活更便捷、更智慧</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>2025年3月，郑州高新区跻身全国高新区第一梯队，国产手术机器人完成全球首例&ldquo;北斗+5G&rdquo;三地远程手术&mdash;&mdash;我国已实现关键核心技术完全自主可控</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>2025年6月，国务院国资委发布40项央企AI高价值场景，推动AI赋能千行百业&mdash;&mdash;科技创新是提升综合国力的战略支撑</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>2025年8月，北京世界机器人大会吸引全球50家人形机器人企业参展，中国专利占比超60%&mdash;&mdash;创新驱动发展，中国智造迈向全球价值链高端</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>2025年，中国科技创新持续突破。以下新闻评述中，错误的是（　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-